y-700 leading-relaxed mb-10\">Run by Ramakrishna Mission Ashrama, Narayanpur, the ITI was established on 01 October 2012 to train unemployed Scheduled Tribe youth of Abujhmarh and nearby tribal areas. It now runs 10 NCVT-affiliated trades with about 350 ST trainees across 20 units, using modern equipment and experienced instructors to enable employment and self-employment.</p><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Engineering trades (NCVT)</h2><div class=\"overflow-x-auto border border-blue-100 rounded-xl\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"navy-gradient text-white\"><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-3\">Trade</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-3\">Duration</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-3\">Seats</th><th class=\"text-left px-4 py-3\">Eligibility</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-blue-50 bg-white\"><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Electrician</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Two Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">40</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3 text-gray-600\">10th pass with Maths &amp; Science</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Draughtsman Civil</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Two Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">48</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3 text-gray-600\">10th pass with Maths &amp; Science</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Fitter</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Two Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">40</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3 text-gray-600\">10th pass with Maths &amp; Science</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Turner</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Two Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">40</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3 text-gray-600\">10th pass with Maths &amp; Science</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Wireman</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">Two Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">40</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3 text-gray-600\">10th pass</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Mason</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">One Year</td><td class=\"px-4 py-3\">48</td><td class